"{\"uid\": \"lowkickmma.com-joe-rogan-scolds-scam-olympics-queens-trans\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"UFC commentator and podcast hostJoe Roganhas taken aim at the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 87, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 3, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378205530074452e-18, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking during an interview, he criticized the organization for being a scam when it comes to money, how they are robbing athletes, and added notes about transexuals, drag queens, and a wacky gay dude.\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The comedian and podcast host Joe Rogan, who has worked alongside the UFC for decades, had some things to say about the 2024 SummerOlympics, which are being hosted in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}, {\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378205530074452e-18, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.937507829580151e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999090990126223, \"rank\": 5.093054619273089e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rogan calls out the Olympics for being a financial scam and is ripping off the athletes.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He explains how all the money goes to the organizers rather than the athletes.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is a giant scam,\\\" Joe Rogan explained on hispodcast, \\\"There are two things going on simultaneously, okay?\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have the best athletes in the world participating in their disciplines.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then on top of that, you have enormous amounts of money being made, and none of it's going to the athletes.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a giant scam.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[H/t MMANews]  \\\"The money they make is astronomical,\\\" he continued, \\\"The Olympics makes billions and billions in television revenue and advertising revenue.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they do not give any of it to the athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joe Rogan is employed by the UFC, a billion-dollar company that has been continuously criticized for poorfighter payand has aclass action lawsuitagainst it.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}, {\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378205530074452e-18, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to the UFC and fighter pay his tone is slightly different.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378205530074452e-18, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rogan, on UFC fighter pay with Luke Thomas,explains, \\\"Do you factor in the overhead?\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Thomas_(footballer,_born_2001)\", \"score\": 0.5671213124017612, \"rank\": 0.39130434782612683, \"text\": \"Luke Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Thomas_(footballer,_born_2001)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Thomas_(footballer,_born_2001)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you factor in all the employees?\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you factor in the machine that's behind the UFC?\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1576, \"end\": 1579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378205530074452e-18, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The UFC has to be profitable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1585, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.378205530074452e-18, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing UFC fighter pay Joe Rogan said, \\\"I think you should get the most amount of money you can possibly get.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's also a business and I think that if they are struggling as much as I think they are - I do not talk finances with them but I know that WME, the people who own it, are hurting, bad.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Webcentral_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.667438666651175e-19, \"text\": \"WME\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Webcentral_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Webcentral_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are laying people off.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most businesses are hurting.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[H/tMMAFighting]  When it comes to theOlympics, Joe Rogan likely has a point especially when it comes to the economics of hosting the Olympic games.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2022, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simply, the numbers do not add up as a benefit for anyone involved, not just the athletes but also the host cities.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have several European cities dropping their bids,\\\" economist Andrew Zimbalist explained in an interview with the New York Times, \\\"Because of a plebiscite or their residents voted, \\\"No, we do not want to do this.\\\"\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Zimbalist\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Zimbalist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Zimbalist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Zimbalist\"}, {\"begin\": 2358, \"end\": 2366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999517968, \"rank\": 2.663267555908291e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are looking at the balance sheet, which is overwhelmingly negative.\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are looking at the social and environmental disruption, which is extremely problematic.\\\"\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He argues that cities that host the Olympics stand to lose tens of billions of dollars.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrew Zimbalist outlines how the Olympics keep the vast amount ofrevenue, nearly eighty percent, for themselves.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Zimbalist\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Zimbalist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Zimbalist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Zimbalist\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cities and athletes do not benefit, but the real winners are development companies.\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some cities, with development costs, stand to lose nearly30 billion dollarsbecause the income for hosting the Olympic games simply is not there.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bullseye chic.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3062, \"end\": 3070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bullseye_with_Jesse_Thorn\", \"score\": 0.9999946984462001, \"rank\": 5.301582106581957e-06, \"text\": \"Bullseye\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bullseye_with_Jesse_Thorn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bullseye_with_Jesse_Thorn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udc85#Paris2024|#Olympics|@issf_official|#ShootingSportpic.twitter.com/q2SWIeBRuL  For Joe Rogan, it's not just about the money.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3161, \"end\": 3164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also brought up transexuals and drag queens,whichisatopichelovestodiscuss.\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When discussing money issues regarding asporting event, Rogan finds a way to talk about LGBTQ people.\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the opening ceremonies, the Olympics were criticized for somecontroversialimages.\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rogan was sensitive about the topic and was clearly triggered by the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The ridiculous opening ceremony,\\\" Rogan added, \\\"Where you got a bunch of drag queens doing the last supper and all that s*** \\u2026 Nobody understands it because it's not made by athletes \\u2026 These are the crazy people who are putting on the last supper with transexuals.\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what they are doing \\u2026 It's not the place for it.\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are pushing this weird agenda in this place where people are already getting f***** over \\u2026 They let some wacky gay dude get ahold of the reins and he decided to do this.\\\"\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 4056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not billions of people all across the world tuning in,\\\" he said, \\\"Just to see a bunch of transexuals pretend to be Jesus and the disciples.\\\"\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4184, \"end\": 4189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.99033196299085, \"rank\": 0.009761633621279688, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khalil Rountree Jr. and Joe Rogan briefly discuss Hitler and the Nazis before finding a way back to the topic.\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4210, \"end\": 4229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khalil_Rountree_Jr.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Khalil Rountree Jr.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khalil_Rountree_Jr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Khalil_Rountree_Jr.\"}, {\"begin\": 4234, \"end\": 4237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"score\": 0.8555864836904831, \"rank\": 0.11199048677574373, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Buck\"}, {\"begin\": 4260, \"end\": 4266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"score\": 0.9999999787210074, \"rank\": 2.1278967194613722e-08, \"text\": \"Hitler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adolf_Hitler\"}, {\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazism\", \"score\": 0.6223218069090019, \"rank\": 0.598740427112982, \"text\": \"Nazis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I like some of the symbolism of the Olympics,\\\" economist Andrew Zimbalistsaid, \\\"I am not sure how penetrating it is, but I like the idea that you bring the world's best athletes together from 205 countries, and you have them compete against each other on the playing field rather than on the battlefield.\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That resonates for me.\", \"from\": 4627, \"to\": 4649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I like it.\", \"from\": 4650, \"to\": 4660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, how far does that take us?\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think very far.\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very expensive symbolism.\\\"\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Timothy Wheaton is a combat sports writer who covers MMA, Kickboxing, and Muay Thai.\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4752, \"end\": 4759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Timothy\", \"score\": 0.9985720756319371, \"rank\": 0.001387696729398321, \"text\": \"Timothy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Timothy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Timothy\"}, {\"begin\": 4760, \"end\": 4767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaton_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9999999991287041, \"rank\": 6.535392423160581e-10, \"text\": \"Wheaton\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaton_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaton_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 4810, \"end\": 4820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kickboxing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\"}, {\"begin\": 4826, \"end\": 4835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r